com.camerontec.catalys.core.session.event

Interface ICatalysEventType


  • public interface ICatalysEventType
    This interface defines all the standard Catalys event type constants.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static int CONFIGURATION_LOADED
      Configuration has been loaded.
      static int CONFIGURATION_UPDATED
      A configuration element has been changed.
      static int DELETED_CONNECTION_POINT
      The connection point has been removed (and all associated objects - eg sessions, connections, session managers etc).

      New ConnectionPoint added.

      Output message sequence number changed.
